           MACRO
&NAME      PERR &TEXT
.* GENERATE ERROR MESSAGE AND WTO Ý PRINT (IF PRINT FILE OPEN)
.* SYSPRINT MUST NOT HAVE ASA Ý MACHINE CHARS:- MUST BE VB ONLY.
           B   TSYS&SYSNDX
MES&SYSNDX WTO &TEXT,ROUTCDE=(2,11),MF=L
TSYS&SYSNDX LA R15,SYSPRINT    ADDRESS SYSPRINT
           TM  48(R15),X'10'   OPEN ?
           BO  USEP&SYSNDX
           WTO MES&SYSNDX,MF=E
           B   E&SYSNDX        BYPASS PUT
USEP&SYSNDX PUT (R15),MES&SYSNDX
E&SYSNDX   EQU *
           MEND
